ClassDef.Name: HttpRequestData

Properties.Name: URL
Properties.Description: The target endpoint of the HTTP request.

Properties.Name: Method
Properties.Description: The HTTP method used for the request.

Properties.Name: Body
Properties.Description: The payload sent with the request.

Properties.Name: Headers
Properties.Description: A table of HTTP headers to include with the request, represented as key-value pairs.

Methods.Name: New
Methods.Description: Creates and returns a new instance of `HttpRequestData`

ClassDef.Description: HttpRequestData represents the data required to construct an HTTP request
